padcms.kiosk.view.action

Class Extractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • padcms.kiosk.view.action.Extractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class Extractor
extends java.lang.Thread
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Extractor is used to extract files in format of zip. It extends Thread and runs in self thread. If file to unzip is not in zip format or damaged, Extractor object delete this file, than sends message to GUI about error, sends message to save state of file had to be downloaded that it is not downloaded than sends message to download file one more time.
